casebody.data:
Carla ABRAHAM, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
FARMERS INSURANCE EXCHANGE, Defendant-Appellee,
and
U.S. Disaster Services, LLC, Doing Business as Service Master Don't Panic, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158479
COA: 335353 Supreme Court of Michigan. November 28, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the stipulation signed by counsel for the parties agreeing to the dismissal of this application for leave to appeal is considered, and the application for leave to appeal is DISMISSED with prejudice and without costs.
